Nandini Kumar
Director | Entrepreneur | Mentor | Fashion & Style Expert
Nandini Kumar is a name synonymous with elegance, vision, and creative
distinction. With a rare ability to merge artistic sensibility with strategic insight, she
has built an extraordinary career that re ects both substance and style. Her
academic grounding in Science and Mathematics, formal training in Fashion
Design in Mumbai, and entrepreneurial education from IIM Bangalore together
form the foundation of a multifaceted journey de ned by innovation, leadership,
and enduring impact.
With over 25 years of experience, Nandini has been instrumental in shaping and
elevating fashion storytelling in India. As one of the early visionaries to introduce
style and design into Indian homes through television, she played a de ning role in
transforming the way fashion was understood, appreciated, and experienced by a
wider audience. Her body of work spans the worlds of fashion, media, and
entertainment, with deep expertise in conceptualizing and executing projects
across reality television, documentaries, lms, and advertising.
Over the years, she has collaborated with an impressive portfolio of distinguished
brands including Rocky Star, FedEx, Parle-G, Paco Rabanne, Hugo Boss,
Shoppers Stop, LIC of India, Jashn Sarees, and Kerala Tourism. Her professional
associations extend to some of the most respected production houses in the
industry, including Bag Films, Siddhant Cinevision, Cinevistaas Limited, Ram
Gopal Varma Entertainment, Maruti Films, and DJ’s – A Creative Unit, as well as
leading television networks such as Sony Entertainment Television, Star Plus, Zee
TV, Elle TV, and Sahara Television.
Her editorial voice and styling expertise have been featured in renowned
publications including Vogue, Women’s Era, Cosmopolitan, Gr8 Magazine,
and Society. She has also styled numerous celebrated personalities, crafting looks
that are distinctive, memorable, and deeply expressive of individuality and grace.
Vision & Mentorship
At the heart of Nandini Kumar’s journey lies an unwavering commitment to
transformation — not only of style, but of people, perspectives, and possibilities.
Her work is de ned by a signature aesthetic that gracefully weaves together
creativity, cultural richness, and contemporary relevance. Beyond her professional
accomplishments, she has remained deeply invested in nurturing emerging talent
and shaping the future of the fashion industry.
This commitment gave rise to NKFA, a platform envisioned to guide aspiring
students beyond the boundaries of conventional education and prepare them for
the dynamic realities of the fashion world. Through thoughtful mentorship, industry
exposure, and practical insight, NKFA empowers young creatives to build careers
that are con dent, purposeful, and future-ready.
Artistic & Social Impact
Deeply inspired by India’s rich artisanal legacy, Nandini has consistently
championed the preservation and celebration of traditional craftsmanship.
Recognizing the importance of sustaining heritage in an ever-evolving world, she
introduced Madhubani art on eco-conscious furnishings, bringing the intricacy and
beauty of Indian craftsmanship to a global audience.
Her passion for art and cultural revival further led to the founding of Artistique
Tale, a platform dedicated to promoting both traditional and contemporary artwhile supporting artisan communities. Extending this philosophy into the realm of
social impact, she also launched The Craft of Mindfulness, an initiative that uses
art and rural craft as meaningful tools for mental health awareness, healing, and
community building among younger generations.
Philosophy & Legacy
Passion, willpower, and resilience continue to de ne Nandini Kumar’s path. She
believes in the power of originality, in standing apart with conviction, and in leaving
behind a meaningful legacy through every endeavour she undertakes.
In a world that is constantly evolving, Nandini Kumar stands as a trailblazer across
fashion, art, mentorship, and wedding curation — a woman of vision whose work
continues to inspire those who aspire to create with purpose, lead with elegance,
and dream without limits.

